                "21": {
                  "id": "21",
                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                  "text": "He's gone. Don't you understand? He's gone!",
                  "context": "NodeContext: In pain more than anger. The player didn't do it on purpose. She's in anguish over losing Wyll to his demonic pact (he was sucked into the Hells after the player killed Mizora). Emotion can be quite intense here.",
